 Hidden Variable (HV): Toss a coin and assign 
\begin_inset Formula $c=+1$
\end_inset

 for heads, else assign 
\begin_inset Formula $c=-1$
\end_inset

.
\begin_inset Newline newline
\end_inset

3.
 Predictions/Assignments: For an operator 
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{p}'\in\{\hat{A}_{ij},\hat{R}_{i},\hat{C}_{j}\,(\forall\,i,j)\}$
\end_inset

