\begin_inset Formula $\lambda$
\end_inset

, s.t.
 
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{p}'\left|\psi\right\rangle =\lambda\left|\psi\right\rangle $
\end_inset

.
 If 
\begin_inset Formula $\exists$
\end_inset

