 Else, find 
\begin_inset Formula $\left|p_{\pm}\right\rangle $
\end_inset

 (eigenkets of 
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{p}$
\end_inset

), s.t.
 
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{p}\left|p_{\pm}\right\rangle =\pm\left|p_{\pm}\right\rangle $
\end_inset

